## Checkout Type Behavior Matrix

| checkoutType | Shipping needed | Address needed | Schedule needed | SDK type field |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| `listings` | ✓ | ✓ (delivery) | ✗ | `listings` |
| `events` | ✗ | ✗ | ✓ | `events` |
| `appointments` | ✗ | ✗ | ✓ | `appointments` |
| `donation` | ✗ | ✗ | ✗ | `donation` |
| `digital` | ✗ | ✗ | ✗ | `digital` |

```ts
const SPECIAL_TYPES  = ['events', 'appointments', 'donation']
const SCHEDULE_TYPES = ['events', 'appointments']

const checkoutType   = items[0]?.listing?.order_type ?? 'listings'
const needsShipping  = !SPECIAL_TYPES.includes(checkoutType) && checkoutType !== 'digital'
const isScheduleType = SCHEDULE_TYPES.includes(checkoutType)
```

