## Addresses

```tsx
// Shipping addresses — authenticated users only
const { data: addressData } = useGetAddressesQuery(undefined, { skip: !isAuthenticated })
const addresses = addressData?.addresses ?? []

// Storage hub pick-up locations — always fetch (needed when type = storage_hub)
const { data: hubData } = useGetStorageHubAddressesQuery()
const storageHubs = hubData?.addresses ?? []

// Auto-select default
const defaultAddress = addresses.find(a => a.default) ?? addresses[0]
```

**Rules:**
- **Never** call `useGetAddressesQuery()` without `{ skip: !isAuthenticated }` — guest API call will error
- Guest users enter address via `guest_name` / `guest_email` fields — no address selection UI
- Storage hub selection replaces delivery address when `selectedShipping.type === 'storage_hub'`
- Storage hub ID goes into `shipping_address_id` in payload (same field as delivery)

