## Sub-Shipment Methods (SendCloud & External)

Both fetched reactively — trigger after user selects shipping method AND delivery address.

```tsx
const isSendCloud = selectedShipping?.channel === 'sendcloud'
const isExternal  = !!(
  selectedShipping?.metadata?.extension_id &&
  selectedShipping?.metadata?.price_list !== false
)

// SendCloud — needs country_code from selected address
const { data: scData } = useGetSendCloudShipmentMethodsQuery(
  { shipping_method_id: selectedShipping.id, country: selectedAddress.country_code },
  { skip: !isSendCloud || !selectedAddress },
)

// External extension — needs address.id
const { data: extData } = useGetExternalShipmentMethodsQuery(
  { shipping_method_id: selectedShipping.id, shipping_address_id: selectedAddress.id },
  { skip: !isExternal || !selectedAddress?.id },
)

// Always reset selectedShipment when either input changes
useEffect(() => { setSelectedShipment(null) }, [selectedShipping?.id, selectedAddress?.id])
```

**In payload:** both use `external_shipping_method_id: selectedShipment.id`

