## Error Codes

| Code | Meaning | Action |
|------|---------|--------|
| `127` | Wallet amount not eligible for payment method | Show error, prompt user to pick different payment method |
| `400` | Validation error (e.g. cart attribute) | Show server message |
| `480` | Cart seller conflict | Clear cart |

